snippet.title: Glenn Beck Says God Has Raised Up Ted Cruz And Is Asking Us To Choose Between Good & Evil

localized.description:
http://www.rightwingwatch.org/content/glenn-beck-says-god-has-raised-ted-cruz-and-asking-us-choose-between-good-evil

Right Wing Watch reports on the extreme rhetoric and activities of key right-wing figures and organizations by showing their views in their own words. In this video, Glenn Beck campaigns for Ted Cruz in Indiana, declaring that God has raised him up, just like George Washington, and is testing the nation to choose between good and evil.
